[467.826824, "o", "assert verdict == \"1\", f\"Expected 1, got {verdict}. Output: {out}\"\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h> print(\"PASS\")\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h> \r\n\u001b[?2004l\r"]
